<plot>This "mockumentary" is an homage to Neo-Burlesque framed around a fictitious retreat, Camp Burlesque. Former Miss Exotic World, Erochica Bamboo is the main attraction, as the camera and narrator follow her doings at this mythical destination, which caters to the stars of today's burlesque. More than 30 sexy "campers" go through their paces, exploring and exploiting the almost-forgotten art of the striptease. Cameos by past stars pay tribute to burlesque through song, comedy and dance. It's Titillating! It's Shocking! It's Camp!</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?091787</url></doc>
